Sentencas: The reoxidation behavior of a Ni-Fe metal anode supported cell using a thin LaGaO3 electrolyte film was investigated as a function of the reoxidation temperature.
Titulo: Reoxidation behavior of Ni-Fe bimetallic anode substrate in solid oxide fuel cells using a thin LaGaO3 based film electrolyte

Sentencas: After oxidation and reduction treatments for 2 h, the voltage did not return to the initial voltage at higher temperatures (773-973 K): however, after reoxidation at 673 K, the cell exhibited almost the same OCV as the as-prepared cell.
Titulo: Reoxidation behavior of Ni-Fe bimetallic anode substrate in solid oxide fuel cells using a thin LaGaO3 based film electrolyte

Sentencas: During reoxidation with air at the higher temperatures, the Ni-Fe metal substrate exhibited two different expansion behaviors by the different oxidation rates of Ni and Fe.
Titulo: Reoxidation behavior of Ni-Fe bimetallic anode substrate in solid oxide fuel cells using a thin LaGaO3 based film electrolyte

Sentencas: On the other hand, the volumetric change of the oxidized substrate at 673 K was negligible.

Sentencas: SEM-EDX results exhibited the reoxidation of Ni-Fe occurred only at the bottom part of the substrate and at the interface between the electrolyte and the substrate.
